Let's look at all four together, because they share the same flawed logic:

The pattern behind all four responses
Their Solution	What They Think It Solves	What It Actually Does
Extra review gate before release	Catches bugs before production	Adds delay at the most expensive point
Lead signs off on every story	Ensures quality through seniority	Creates bottleneck, doesn't scale, false confidence
